; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE7F4AF8D29FFE7B176FC8EFB33FC3D" author="Alves, D. F. R. &amp; Lima, D. J. M. &amp; Hirose, G. L. &amp; Martinez, P. A. &amp; Dolabella, S. S. &amp; Barros-Alves, S. P." box="[1035,1233,871,897]" pageId="17" pageNumber="206" pagination="41 - 55" refId="ref16601" refString="Alves, D. F. R., Lima, D. J. M., Hirose, G. L., Martinez, P. A., Dolabella, S. S. &amp; Barros-Alves, S. P. (2018) Morphological and molecular analyses confirm the occurrence of two sympatric Lysmata shrimp (Crustacea, Decapoda) in the southwestern Atlantic. Zootaxa, 4526 (1), 41 - 55. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4526.1.3" type="journal article" year="2018">
