</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE7F4AF8D29FFE7B1A0FC8EFAFBFC3D" author="Alves, D. F. R. &amp; Lopez Greco, L. S. &amp; Barros-Alves, S. P. &amp; Hirose, G. L." box="[1245,1305,871,897]" pageId="17" pageNumber="206" pagination="1 - 18" refId="ref16694" refString="Alves, D. F. R., Lopez Greco, L. S., Barros-Alves, S. P. &amp; Hirose, G. L. (2019) Sexual system, reproductive cycle and embryonic development of the red-striped shrimp Lysmata vittata, an invader in the western Atlantic Ocean. PLoS ONE, 14, 1 - 18. https: // doi. org / 10.1371 / journal. pone. 0210723" type="journal article" year="2019">2019</bibRefCitation>
), as well as individuals cited as “ 
